# Changelog
## Instructions to Add More Entries
To add more entries, first add five hyphens, the update name, and five more hyphens, like so: -----Alpha 0.1-----. Then, mention all that was added in the update,
using these tags:
ADD: Added a feature.
UPDATE: Updated or improved a feature.
REMOVE: Removed a feature.
OPTIMISE: Optimised a feature.
BUGFIX: Fixed a bug in a feature.

## Changelog
-----Alpha 0.3.1-----
ADD: Added map lighting
ADD: Added sky colored background panel

-----Alpha 0.3-----
ADD: Added an ore generator.
ADD: Added the main menu.

-----Alpha 0.2-----
ADD: Added fractal-noise-based map generation.
UPDATE: Improved the player controller.
